Make sure to sync settings between IDEs. You can do this by following steps here:
https://www.jetbrains.com/help/pycharm/sharing-your-ide-settings.html#IDE_settings_sync

Or: Enable setting sync on original IDE (push settings) -> on new IDE enable settins sync (get settings)

# Black auto formatting
Follow directions here (maybe have to specify real path to black binary):
https://akshay-jain.medium.com/pycharm-black-with-formatting-on-auto-save-4797972cf5de
